Using this cardset
------------------

The cardset is in the drawer Batman. You should copy
this drawer to the cards-drawer in the Marryampic-dir.
I have tried to design pics in an unique manner. For the
samples this way was very difficult. The samples are in
english language, because of taken from original sequences.
(Thanks to Iain).
If anyone has better samples or pics, he can send it to me,
please. I like emails and you can support me for more
cardsets. You can send me more pics and samples for various
themes.

