Some Bugs
---------

If you choose a screenmode like NTSC or similar
(p.e. 640x400), the sample playing are too fast.

This bug is fixed now. It occurs by a worse save
setting at PPaint.

in previous carsets:

The pics are saved in Picassomode instead of
PAL:Highres-Interlace. Thanks to Dave.
In the 256 color version was the second color
very dark. The colours for mousepointer and
menue were wrong. Thanks to MaVati.

All bugs now REALLY fixed.


